\Delta Cp^{i} = f_{prf\_recv} \cdot \Delta \epsilon^{i}_{exit} = f_{prf\_recv} \cdot f_{strn\_rlf} \cdot \epsilon^{i}_{exit}  下一机架入口的单位凸度如下公式所示。  
Cp^{i+1}_{entry} =Cp^{i}_{exit} - \Delta Cp^{i} = Cp^{i}_{exit}  - f_{prf\_recv} \cdot f_{strn\_rlf} \cdot \epsilon^{i}_{exit}

